params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TYP\\" as \\"WH_TYP\\", " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_ADDR1\\" as \\"WH_ADDR1\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_ADDR2\\" as \\"WH_ADDR2\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TEL\\" as \\"WH_TEL\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_PERSON\\" as \\"WH_PERSON\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_INSIDE_FLG\\" as \\"WH_INSIDE_FLG\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_OUTSIDE_FLG\\" as \\"WH_OUTSIDE_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_WH, " +" ( " +" select " +" VEND_CD, " +" VEND_ANAME " +" from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" ) M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\"(+) = M_WH.VEND_CD " +" and M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"insert into " +" M_WH(\\"WH_CD\\", \\"WH_NAME\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"WH_TYP\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"MRP_FLG\\", \\"WH_ADDR1\\", \\"WH_ADDR2\\", \\"WH_TEL\\", \\"WH_PERSON\\", \\"WH_INSIDE_FLG\\", \\"WH_OUTSIDE_FLG\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?,( " +" select " +" COMPANY_CD " +" from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" ))"

"select " +" count(*) as \\"COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_WH, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" VEND_CD = ? " +" and WH_CD != ? " +" and M_WH.COMPANY_CD = SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD " +" and PLANT_CD = ? " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"

"select " +" count(*) as \\"COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" VEND_CD = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD = SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"

"select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TYP\\" as \\"WH_TYP\\", " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\" as \\"MRP_FLG\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_ADDR1\\" as \\"WH_ADDR1\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_ADDR2\\" as \\"WH_ADDR2\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_TEL\\" as \\"WH_TEL\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_PERSON\\" as \\"WH_PERSON\\", " +" M_WH.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\"(+) = M_WH.VEND_CD " +" and M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"SELECT " +" COUNT(WH_INSIDE_FLG) " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND WH_CD <> ? " +" AND WH_INSIDE_FLG = 1"
"SELECT " +" COUNT(WH_OUTSIDE_FLG) " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND WH_CD <> ? " +" AND WH_OUTSIDE_FLG = 1"
"SELECT " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" AS \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ISSUE_INST.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" MW.WH_CD as WH_CD " +"from " +" M_WH MW " +"where " +" MW.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and MW.WH_TYP = 40"
